<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{أَكْبَرُ}</span> <span class="c4">[٤٥]</span> كاف،<span class="c5"> أي:</span> ولذكر الله إياكم أكبر من ذكركم إياه، قاله ابن عباس <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>{مَا تَصْنَعُونَ <span class="c2">(٤٥)</span>} <span class="c4">[٤٥]</span> تام.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{إِلَّا بِالَّتِي هِيَ أَحْسَنُ}</span> <span class="c4">[٤٦]</span> ليس بوقف؛ للاستثناء بعده.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c3">{ظَلَمُوا مِنْهُمْ}</span> <span class="c4">[٤٦]</span> كاف.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c3">{وَأُنْزِلَ إِلَيْكُمْ}</span> <span class="c4">[٤٦]</span> حسن،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span> <span class="c2">«وإلاهكم واحد»</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>{وَنَحْنُ لَهُ مُسْلِمُونَ <span class="c2">(٤٦)</span>} <span class="c4">[٤٦]</span> كاف.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c3">{إِلَيْكَ الْكِتَابَ}</span> <span class="c4">[٤٧]</span> حسن؛ لأنَّ فـ <span class="c2">«الذين»</span> مبتدأ، و <span class="c2">«يؤمنون به»</span> خبر.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>و <span class="c3">{بِهِ}</span> <span class="c4">[٤٧]</span> جائز، فصلًا بين الفريقين.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c3">{وَمِنْ هَؤُلَاءِ مَنْ يُؤْمِنُ بِهِ}</span> <span class="c4">[٤٧]</span> كاف؛ للابتداء بالنفي.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>{الْكَافِرُونَ <span class="c2">(٤٧)</span>} <span class="c4">[٤٧]</span> تام.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c3">{بِيَمِينِكَ}</span> <span class="c4">[٤٨]</span> قيل: جائز، وليس بحسن؛<span class="c5"> لأنَّ الذي بعده في تأويل الجواب كأنَّه قال:</span> لو كنت تتلو كتابًا، أو كتبت بيمينك لارتاب المبطلون.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>و {الْمُبْطِلُونَ <span class="c2">(٤٨)</span>} <span class="c4">[٤٨]</span> تام.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c3">{الْعِلْمَ}</span> <span class="c4">[٤٩]</span> كاف.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>{الظَّالِمُونَ <span class="c2">(٤٩)</span>} <span class="c4">[٤٩]</span> كاف.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c3">{آَيَاتٌ مِنْ رَبِّهِ}</span> <span class="c4">[٥٠]</span> كاف.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c3">{عِنْدَ اللَّهِ}</span> <span class="c4">[٥٠]</span> جائز.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>{مُبِينٌ <span class="c2">(٥٠)</span>} <span class="c4">[٥٠]</span> تام.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c3">{يُتْلَى عَلَيْهِمْ}</span> <span class="c4">[٥١]</span> كاف، وتام عند أبي حاتم.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>{يؤمنون <span class="c2">(٥١)</span>} <span class="c4">[٥١]</span> تام.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span class="c3">{شَهِيدًا}</span> <span class="c4">[٥٢]</span> صالح؛ لأنَّ ما بعده يصلح وصفًا واستئنافًا.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span><span class="c3">{وَالْأَرْضِ}</span> <span class="c4">[٥٢]</span> كاف؛ لأنَّ <span class="c2">«والذين»</span> مبتدأ،<span class="c5"> خبره:</span> <span class="c2">«أولئك»</span>.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span><span class="c3">{وَكَفَرُوا بِاللَّهِ}</span> <span class="c4">[٥٢]</span> ليس بوقف؛ لأنَّ خبر <span class="c2">«الذين»</span> لم يأت.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>{الْخَاسِرُونَ <span class="c2">(٥٢)</span>} <span class="c4">[٥٢]</span> تام.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span><span class="c3">{بالعذاب}</span> <span class="c4">[٥٣]</span> حسن في الموضعين.<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span><span class="c3">{الْعَذَابُ}</span> <span class="c4">[٥٣]</span> كاف.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
